question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Mikä on Gyeongjun kaupungintalon sijainti Gyeongjussa, Etelä-Koreassa?
answer: Gyeongjun kaupungintalo sijaitsee osoitteessa 16 Cheongun 3-gil, Dongcheon-dong, Gyeongju, Gyeongsangbuk-do, Etelä-Korea.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located at 16 Cheongun 3-gil, Dongcheon-dong, Gyeongju, Gyeongsangbuk-do, South Korea.
